    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine runs consistently, and the transmission shifts through all gears, but you may notice some minor vibrations at highway speeds. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows clear signs of wear on the upholstery and carpet. It is a solid, functional car for anyone needing dependable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 18500.0,
