    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a source for quality parts? This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast ready to bring a car back to life! While it is currently in poor condition and will need some significant TLC and repair work, it's priced to move and offers a great foundation for your next automotive adventure. Grab this bargain and start your restoration journey today!",
      "price": 3800.0,
